    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #M">Index XIX.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index X.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Index XVIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XVIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Index XIX., in quo regnum Caroli primi explicatur</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XVIII. de Carolo I. rege regnoque per illum aucto</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Post haec missus Gentilis sacrosanctae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Romanae ecclesiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Romane ecclesie</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">presbiter</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">presbyter</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">praesbyter</rdg>
                    </app> cardinalis ab apostolica sede legatus ita persuasit Hungaris, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(depositis odiis sublatisque simultatibus)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">depositis odiis sublatisque <app>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">simultatibus</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#Z">simulatibus</rdg>
                            </app></rdg>
                    </app> absque ulla reluctatione Carolum regem susciperent.</s>
                <s n="2">Acto itaque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Albae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Albe</rdg>
                    </app> omnium optimatum conventu <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">summa</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">suma</rdg>
                    </app> cum omnium laetitia regni coronam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">accepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">accaepit</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">1–2 = Th 2.89.</note></s>
                <s n="3">Magna cum laude regnum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">hic suum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">suum hic</rdg>
                    </app> tenuit annos duos et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">XL-ta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quadraginta</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">3 = Th 2.99.</note></s>
                <s n="4">Tres duxit uxores, Mariam natione Polonam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Cazimerii</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Casimiri</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Casimiri</rdg>
                    </app> ducis filiam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #M">Beatricem filiam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2 #S3"/>
                    </app> regis Romanorum, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Elisabectam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Elisabettam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2">Elizabetham</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Elisabetham</rdg>
                    </app> filiam Ladislai regis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Poloniae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Polonie</rdg>
                    </app>, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">illae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">ille</rdg>
                    </app> absque ulla sobolis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">susceptione</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">suscaeptione</rdg>
                    </app> decesserunt, ex hac vero <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">suscepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">suscaepit</rdg>
                    </app> filios quatuor, Carolum, Ladislaum, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Laim</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Loym</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Loim</rdg>
                    </app>, qui et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Lodovicus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ludovicus</rdg>
                    </app> nominatus est, et Andream.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">4 = Th
                        2.91–92, 94–95.</note></s>
                <s n="5">Quidam e suis domesticis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Felicianus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">Foelicianus</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Faelicianus</rdg>
                    </app> nomine maligno adductus furore paravit insidias, quibus ipsum una et
                    reginam ac eorum liberos interimeret, sed patrari <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #M">tam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3"/>
                    </app> execrabile facinus non est passa divina benignitas, detectae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app> insidiae fuere, idcirco debitas <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(iubente rege)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">iubente rege</rdg>
                    </app> dedit pro tentato scelere <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">poenas</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">paenas</rdg>
                    </app>, de ipso enim deque sibi necessitudine coniunctis supplicium <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">sumptum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sumtum</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">5 = Th 2.96.</note></s>
                <s n="6">Bellum gerens adversus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Matheum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Matthaeum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Mattheum</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1">Trinchinium</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2 #S3 #M">Trenchinium</rdg>
                    </app> hominem genere nobilem et armis opibusque potentem, qui Hungariam armis
                    infestabat, illius ingentem exercitum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">proelio</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">praelio</rdg>
                    </app> vicit.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">6 = Th 2.90.</note></s>
                <s n="7">Regnum suum prudentia rebusque fortissime gestis non conservavit modo
                    tutatusque est, sed auxit etiam plurimum, copias instructas atque expeditas non
                    solum bello sed pace quoque semper habuit, ut <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1">quotiens</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #S2 #S3 #M">quoties</rdg>
                    </app> rerum exigeret necessitas, praesto essent, ita ingens facta est eius apud <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cunctas</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">cuntas</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2">paene</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S3 #M">pene</rdg>
                    </app> orbis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">terrae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">terre</rdg>
                    </app> nationes auctoritas.</s>
                <s n="8">Sua <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">ditione</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">ditioni</rdg>
                    </app> tenuit Dalmatiam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Croatiam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Croaciam</rdg>
                    </app>, Serviam, Lodomeriam, Russiam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #M">Cumaniam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Cumiam</rdg>
                    </app>, Bulgariam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Bosnam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Bosniam</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="9">Vixit Christianissime, ideoque multis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Christiano</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Chrisciano</rdg>
                    </app> homine dignis virtutibus ornatus inter orbis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">principes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">principis</rdg>
                    </app> non mediocriter enituit.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">7–9 = Th
                        2.99.</note></s>
                <s n="10">Erexit aedem apud Lippam in honorem sancti <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #M">Lodovici</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Ludovici</rdg>
                    </app> ordinis fratrum minorum, qui eius fuerat frater, constituit et ibidem
                    coenobium, in quo eiusdem ordinis sacerdotes deo famularentur.<note
                        type="critic" corresp="RKK">10 = Th 2.93. – <hi rend="italic">eius fuerat
                            frater</hi>: error e nimia abbreviatione; apud Thuróczy: „fuit frater
                        carnalis patris sui“.</note></s>
                <s n="11">Albae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">beatae Mariae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">beate Marie</rdg>
                    </app> virginis aedem, quae saepe conflagrare <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2">antea</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ante</rdg>
                    </app> solebat, plumbeis texit laminis, cumque postea ipso vivente etiam
                    conflagrasset, plumbo ipsam denuo texit.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">11 =
                        Th 2.94.</note></s>
                <s n="12">Obiit anno <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">humanae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">humane</rdg>
                    </app> salutis MCCCXLII. XVII. Calendas Augusti, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Albaeque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Albae</rdg>
                    </app> sepultus est.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">12 = Th 2.99.</note></s>
            </p>
